Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.12,0:22:24.46,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}We are tossed by the waves of pain and tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.46,0:22:28.27,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}I'm tossed into the fray tossed by various fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.27,0:22:29.92,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}Wake up your brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.92,0:22:32.05,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}Flashed in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:34.56,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}It's a burst of sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:40.90,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}諦めがくれた安楽 沈滯の世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.90,0:22:46.86,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}いつからだっただろうふいに輝き始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.86,0:22:50.15,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}変わらずにいてと願うこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.15,0:22:53.85,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}変わりゆく時に生きる僕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:56.91,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}本當の聲を言う得る夢を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:01.45,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}君と繋がった空へ響かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.91,0:23:05.35,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}もっと強くこの両手で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.35,0:23:08.63,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}涙全て振り払えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.63,0:23:11.91,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}“今度こそは”呟く今と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:15.09,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}傷さえも無駄にしない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:18.49,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}もっと早く君のもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.49,0:23:21.78,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}たとえ羽根が千切れようとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.78,0:23:25.07,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}歪む世界 走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.07,0:23:28.35,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}感覚のその向うへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.35,0:23:34.12,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5\fad(0,800)}真実と加速してく
